text: Live at the Half Note may refer to: * Live at the Half-Note, a 1964 album by Art Farmer's Quartet * Live at the Half Note (Lee Konitz album), recorded in 1959, released in 1994 * Live at the Half Note: One Down, One Up, a 2005 compilation of 1965 radio broadcasts from the Half Note Club ==See also== * At the Half Note Cafe, a 1960 album by Donald Byrd
title: Live at the Half Note
